{"type":null,"faqId":7624,"title":"如何添加/删除/查看/发送电子邮件？","answer":"<p>进入主菜单-&gt;电子邮件-&gt;登录帐号<br />登陆账号分为手动设置和自动设置<br />1. 手动设置：<br />输入账号和密码-&gt;点击POP3-&gt;进入接收服务器设置界面，在POP3服务器中添加POP3.-&gt;点击下一步-&gt;在外发服务器设置界面添加smtp. -&gt;点击下一步-&gt;在账户选项界面可选择收件箱检查频率-&gt;点击下一步-&gt;进入设置电子邮件界面-&gt;输入为此账户创建名称和您的姓名-&gt;点击完成。<br />2. 自动设置：<br />输入账号和密码-&gt;直接点击下一步-&gt;直接进入设置电子邮件界面-&gt;点击完成。</p>\n<p><img width=\"316\" height=\"393\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/0-120214104155.PNG\" /></p>\n<p>进入Email-&gt;按菜单键-&gt;帐户-&gt;在要删除的帐户上长按，选择删除帐户。</p>\n<p><img width=\"317\" height=\"415\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/1-120214104207.PNG\" /></p>\n<p>按菜单键-&gt;撰写-&gt;编辑一封邮件即可发。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7764","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1324546359000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":197,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}